eZpedia extension README

What is the eZpedia extension?
================================

eZpedia is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides commandline script, module views,
kernel overrides classes, design templates and
settings that make up the wiki site http://ezpedia.org


eZpedia version
=======================

The current version of BC Image Alias is 0.7.0
Last Major update: May 07, 2013

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.7.0


